title: For Sale:  John Deere JD 140 H1 Lawn tractor (mower) - (Edmond)
postcontent:
FFor sale is an excellent 1968 John Deere 140 H1 hydrostatic transmission lawn tractor. It has a 44" hydraulic deck with good belts and sharp blades, front hydraulic ports (for a snow / dirt plow) and over size rear lawn tires. It also comes with a Brinly (sleeve hitch for a garden plow, tiller, or de-thatcher) that is hydraulically controlled. It has a 14 hp Kohler cast iron engine (don't let the hp confuse you, it has tons of torque and will out perform a 24 hp modern engine) and independent right and left side rear brakes. title: For Sale:  Custom Remington 700 - .17 fireball; .308; .300 win mag; .338 lapua
postcontent:
Offering a custom built Remington 700 in your choice of caliber - anything from .17 fireball to .308 to .300 win mag; .338 win mag; or .338 Lapua.  You tell us the caliber/contour/ twist and we build from there.  If you need an action to build we have that covered - short, long; small bolt face, standard and mag bolt face bolts.  If we use your existing action/bolt I can blueprint your action/bolt and supply you with a Shilen barrel in your choice of caliber, contour, twist rate and length for 800.  If you need an action/bolt we can offer barreled actions starting at 1200 with a Shilen match grade chrome barrel or 1400 with a stainless match grade barrel.  .338 Lapua barreled actions start at 2300 using Stiller; Defiance; or Surgeon action/bolts.

Each action will be trued up on a lathe the inner lugs trued as well.  The bolt lugs and the bolt face will be squared and trued.  All work is done on a lathe and are cut to precision with a single point cutter.

Once the action and bolt have been blueprinted they will be matted to your choice of barrel.  Shilen, Krieger, Bartlein, Rock Creek, ect...  the barrel will be threaded, breeched, head spaced, crowned and can be threaded for a break.

We can build a barreled action that can be sold with or without a stock.  Your choice of stock: Bell and Carlson, HS precision, McMillan, ect.  We offer pillar bedding and free floated barrels.

Each build is different and is built to your specs.  Cost of your build will vary depending on parts and features for your build.  We have plenty of short actions; long actiins as well as magnum actions if you prefer the magnum calibers.  Just let me know what caliber you would want and we can build it!

The last pic is of factory ammo off the shelf hunting rounds during the break in period...
